				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-15e2db4e elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="15e2db4e" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default">
					<h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default"> Automatic deodorant filling machine</h2>				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-2bec6fdf elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider" data-id="2bec6fdf" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="divider.default">
							<div class="elementor-divider">
			<span class="elementor-divider-separator">
						</span>
		</div>
						</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-3bc5def7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="3bc5def7" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
									<p>Npack deodorant filling machine is one type of filling equipement, which adapts with advance hot filling technology,the working process is typically hot-fill,the solid formula is melted, then dispensed into the empty stick barrel, after filling,a cooling station(cooling tunnel) solidifies it before capping. Precise volume control is usually achieved with a piston filler.The piston is also driven by a servo motor.</p><p>The machine designed for faste changeovers between different container sizes and product lines;Easy operation and cleaning.It is suitable for filling hot liquid or viscous liquid.</p>								</div>
