		<div id="e-n-tab-content-735446502" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="e-n-tab-title-735446502" data-tab-index="2" style="--n-tabs-title-order: 2;" class=" elementor-element elementor-element-9e80fb4 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="9e80fb4" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-b751173 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="b751173" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
									<p>The bag sticker labeling machine is designed with precision and adaptability labeling, features several standout characteristics to cater to a variety of packaging requirements, and it mainly consist of 3 parts: pouch or bag automatic feeder, vacuum conveyor belt, and labeling applicator.</p><ul><li>Precision Label Placement and Fast Feeding: The machine is powered by Panasonic or Siemens servo motors and PLC control, guaranteeing labels are applied accurately, free from wrinkles or air bubbles. It keeps a steady pace, applying each label in the exact same position, so your packaging always looks professional and consistent.</li><li>Widely Application Range: Capable of labeling a diverse array of bag types, such as flat, stand-up, and angle-supported bags, ensuring wide application scope.<br />Flexible Labeling Options: Offers the versatility to apply labels on various parts of the bag including the front, back, top, bottom, or sides, aligning with specific packaging designs.</li><li>Adaptable to Various Label Sizes and Shapes: Supports a range of label dimensions and forms, from standard rectangles and circles to custom shapes, to meet different packaging demands.</li><li>Ease of Use: Equipped with a Siemens color HMI for straightforward adjustments to label specifications and placement, enhancing user experience.</li><li>High Quality Construction: Made from 304/316 stainless steel, it meets GMP standards for cleanliness and durability.<br />Customizable Settings: Allows for adjustment of labeling height and angle, as well as the speed of the conveyor belt and labeling, complemented by a label counter for efficient operation, maintenance simplicity, and prolonged service life.<br />This machine’s combination of accuracy, flexibility, and ease of operation makes it an essential tool for industries ranging from food and beverages to pharmaceuticals and chemicals, streamlining their packaging processes with efficiency and reliability.</li></ul><p>If you’re looking to eliminate inconsistent results, wasted time, or the hassle of manual labeling, upgrading to an automatic pouch bag labeling machine is a smart investment in the future of your packaging line.</p>								</div>
