									<ol><li>Ribbon Coding Machine: Can print production date and batch number.</li><li>Industrial Zebra Engine: For transcoding printing, docking with system software, and integrated real-time printing functionality.</li><li>Transparent Label Detection: Compatible with all label types, including gilded, transparent, paper, or composite S material labels. No need to replace sensors when switching label types. Transparent label detection on the lower lining of transparent labels.</li><li>Visual Inspection Removal: Detects label presence and verifies printed information, batch numbers, and content correctness.</li><li>Heat Transfer Intelligent Coding Machine: Prints QR codes, barcodes, production dates, batch numbers, and more on label paper, enabling product traceability and anti-counterfeiting measures.</li></ol>								</div>
